The Telegraph - Calcutta : Nation

 OBC quota hearing

 New Delhi, July 16: The Supreme Court will tomorrow hear the Centres plea to lift the stay on OBC reservation in institutes of higher learning, reports our special correspondent. 

 Central universities as well as the IITs and IIMs would come under the quota law that the apex court stalled this year as it was still deliberating on the validity of the legislation.




